多少人娶媳婦兒？」<br />\n<br />\n2016年兩會，習近平參加湖南代表團審議時，向代表了解十八洞村的情況。習近平正式提出「精準扶貧」就是在十八洞村。他關切地詢問：「去年有多少人<span style=\"color: red;\">娶媳婦兒</span>？「條件比十八洞村還差的有多少？」「不如它的有多少？」"},{"pid":"16065aee1abd7ff06d250dcf157969bef49ced0f","tid":893021,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:34:36.000Z","msg":"原聲 習近平關心扶貧 問去年有多少人娶媳婦 - YouTube<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HW_q3mDKeuw&amp;app=desktop\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHW_q3mDKeuw%26app%3Ddesktop&d=VSeDE8ZXGasK5mTbQXGUx8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=da9047f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HW_q3mDKeuw&amp;app=desktop</a>"},{"pid":"29ac57450e1b50b8ae9e2024610d66f329d1886a","tid":893021,"uid":116471,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:37:35.000Z","msg":"證據確鑿，考評局表示習近平用錯中文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cccb80a56bf2c5aba99547a71bebf0239f57a0d","tid":893021,"uid":31946,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:37:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 一個錯既用法都要中港融合？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a44010b35d38346e5debd38850687a9119fb6f","tid":893021,"uid":4330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:38:48.000Z","msg":"習近平考dse咪錯囉on9"},{"pid":"5dc244837f467a34df455b81f8d48822614f7a37","tid":893021,"uid":14918,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"8cccb80a56bf2c5aba99547a71bebf0239f57a0d","tid":893021,"uid":31946,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:37:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 一個錯既用法都要中港融合？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" cla